    {
      "title": "FY2025 10-K Analysis",
      "note_type": null,
      "date": "2026-04-04",
      "quarter": null,
      "tags": [
        "strategy",
        "growth"
      ],
      "rating": 3,
      "active": true,
      "content": "[Financial Performance]\nKeysight FY2025 revenue $5.38B (+8.0% recovery from $4.98B trough). Net income $0.85B. FY2024 weakness from telecom/semiconductor inventory correction. FY2025 recovery powered by Spirent, Synopsys OSG, and Ansys PowerArtist acquisitions. Backlog grew to $2.7B from $2.4B.\n[Strategic Priorities]\n• Invest to deliver differentiated, first-to-market solutions\n• Grow recurring revenue through software/services content\n• Capitalize on AI ecosystem opportunities\n[Management Tone]\nBullish",
      "source_doc": null
    },
    {
      "title": "FY2025 vs FY2024 — Narrative Evolution Analysis",
      "note_type": null,
      "date": "2026-04-04",
      "quarter": null,
      "tags": [
        "strategy"
      ],
      "rating": 3,
      "active": true,
      "content": "[Narrative Drift]\nNarrative stable with continued emphasis on innovation and acquisition-driven growth. FY2025 introduces significant new emphasis on AI opportunities. Completed acquisitions: Spirent, OSG, PowerArtist.\n[Risk Evolution]\nImproving: removed 'reduced access to credit' and 'changes in interest rates' risks. No new risks introduced.",
      "source_doc": null
    }
  ],
  "quotes": [
    {
      "quote": "With a software- and customer-centric focus, we continue to make strategic investments to help our customers and partners address their most complex technology challenges.",
      "quote_th": "ด้วยการมุ่งเน้นด้านซอฟต์แวร์และลูกค้า เรายังคงลงทุนเชิงกลยุทธ์เพื่อช่วยลูกค้าและพาร์ทเนอร์ในการรับมือกับความท้าทายทางเทคโนโลยีที่ซับซ้อนที่สุดในทุกช่วงวงจรชีวิตผลิตภัณฑ์",
      "date": "2025-12-17",
      "quarter": null,
      "segment": null,
      "speaker": "Keysight Technologies (Company)",
      "source": "FY2025 10-K",
      "tag": "strategy",
      "sub_tags": [],
      "sentiment": null,
      "analyst_note": null,
      "source_doc": null
    },
    {
      "quote": "Keysight is enabling rapid advances in AI through solutions to increase the efficiency of AI compute clusters, accelerate AI chip development, and support AI-driven network innovation.",
      "quote_th": "Keysight ช่วยเร่งความก้าวหน้าอย่างรวดเร็วใน AI ผ่านเซ็นชุดเพิ่มประสิทธิภาพ AI compute cluster, เร่งการพัฒนาชิป AI และสนับสนุนนวัตกรรมเครือข่ายที่ขับเคลื่อนด้วย AI",
      "date": "2025-12-17",
      "quarter": null,
      "segment": null,
      "speaker": "Keysight Technologies (Company)",
      "source": "FY2025 10-K",
